query: SELECT c.id, c.name, COUNT(DISTINCT cp.id) as phone_count, COUNT(DISTINCT ce.id) as email_count FROM contacts c LEFT JOIN contactPhones cp ON c.id = cp.contactId LEFT JOIN contactEmails ce ON c.id = ce.contactId GROUP BY c.id, c.name LIMIT 10;
